#### Styling Customization

Style the component only through its documented `--mds-{{componentNameWithNoPrefix}}-*` CSS custom properties. Use the Magma color tokens via `rgb(var(--<token>))` so dark mode and high-contrast modes keep working - see [`docs/TOKENS.md`](../../../../../../docs/TOKENS.md).

```css
.my-{{componentNameWithNoPrefix}} {
  /* --mds-{{componentNameWithNoPrefix}}-... properties go here */
}
```
